{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.680", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.280", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.520", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verehrte Zuschauer! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.200", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich hatte genau wie die Kollegin Sitte in meinen B\u00fcrgersprechstunden in den vergangenen Monaten Besuch von Frauen und M\u00e4nnern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.400", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich selbstst\u00e4ndig gemacht haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.880", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aus ganz unterschiedlichen Motiven, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.120", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in ganz unterschiedlichen Branchen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.600", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber sie waren alle mit einem ganz konkreten Problem bei mir: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.000", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihre Krankenversicherungsbeitr\u00e4ge sind zu hoch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.360", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie sich nicht am tats\u00e4chlichen Einkommen orientieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.440", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern an einer fiktiven Gr\u00f6\u00dfe. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.560", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Thema ist gar nicht neu."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.000", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben in der vergangenen Wahlperiode als SPD-Fraktion in einem Positionspapier zu Solo-Selbstst\u00e4ndigen gefordert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.640", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass da etwas passiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.640", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insofern bin ich froh, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.960", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich im Koalitionsvertrag unsere Idee wiederfindet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.080", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben vereinbart, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.760", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Bemessungsgrundlage zu halbieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.360", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dadurch k\u00f6nnen die Beitr\u00e4ge deutlich gesenkt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.800", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hilft vielen Menschen ganz konkret."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.680", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Zahl der Solo-Selbstst\u00e4ndigen ist in den vergangenen Jahren gestiegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.240", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb ger\u00e4t ihre Absicherung bei Krankheit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.800", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alter und Arbeitslosigkeit zu Recht ins Blickfeld. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.560", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da m\u00fcssen wir ran. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.680", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb bin ich froh, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.840", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir heute dar\u00fcber reden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.920", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rund 3\u00a0Millionen Selbstst\u00e4ndige haben keine obligatorische Absicherung im Alter. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.920", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ehemals Selbstst\u00e4ndige sind schon jetzt bei den Beziehern der Grundsicherung deutlich \u00fcberrepr\u00e4sentiert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.680", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verglichen mit ihrem Anteil an der Bev\u00f6lkerung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.440", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit das klar ist: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.240", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht \u00fcberhaupt nicht darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.600", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "irgendjemanden zu bevormunden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.920", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht auch nicht um Planwirtschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.800", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Schimke. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.600", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.600", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frauen und M\u00e4nner, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.440", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich selbstst\u00e4ndig machen wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.960", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so weit wie m\u00f6glich dabei zu unterst\u00fctzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.960", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gleichzeitig hat die so oft bem\u00fchte Eigenverantwortung aber Grenzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.840", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sie erkennbar zulasten der Allgemeinheit geht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.080", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Koalitionsvertrag\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.960", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist schon angesprochen worden\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.960", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben wir deshalb eine Altersvorsorgepflicht f\u00fcr alle Selbstst\u00e4ndigen vereinbart, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.520", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die nicht anderweitig obligatorisch abgesichert sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.400", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben k\u00fcnftig die Wahlm\u00f6glichkeit zwischen der gesetzlichen Rentenversicherung und anderen Vorsorgearten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.440", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese m\u00fcssen allerdings einige Qualit\u00e4tskriterien erf\u00fcllen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.800", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will an dieser Stelle \u00fcberhaupt keinen Hehl daraus machen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.800", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Uns w\u00e4re es am liebsten gewesen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.200", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir h\u00e4tten eine Pflichtmitgliedschaft f\u00fcr Selbstst\u00e4ndige in der gesetzlichen Rentenversicherung hinbekommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.200", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das war leider mit der Union nicht zu machen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.280", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das finde ich schade; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.600", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn die Rentenversicherung ist ein Angebot, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.520", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das auch f\u00fcr Selbstst\u00e4ndige jede Menge Vorteile bietet: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.240", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei der Erwerbsminderung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.080", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei der Hinterbliebenenversorgung und beim Zugang zu Rehaleistungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.240", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das als Selbstst\u00e4ndiger anderweitig abzusichern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.880", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "d\u00fcrfte\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.760", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "erst recht mit kleinem Einkommen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.760", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schwierig werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.800", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich setze deshalb darauf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.800", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass viele Selbstst\u00e4ndige rasch erkennen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.760", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie attraktiv die gesetzliche Rentenversicherung auch f\u00fcr sie ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.480", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit auch das klar ist: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.880", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es bleibt f\u00fcr uns dabei, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.880", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir am Ziel einer Erwerbst\u00e4tigenversicherung festhalten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.480", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit ihr w\u00e4re ein Wechsel zwischen abh\u00e4ngiger Besch\u00e4ftigung und Selbstst\u00e4ndigkeit ohne Probleme m\u00f6glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.840", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne dass Schutz und Anspr\u00fcche verloren gingen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.080", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Wechsel zwischen abh\u00e4ngiger Besch\u00e4ftigung und Selbstst\u00e4ndigkeit wird in Zukunft wahrscheinlich zunehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.600", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb sollten wir auch Selbstst\u00e4ndigen insgesamt den Zugang zur Arbeitslosenversicherung erleichtern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.760", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ulla Schmidt wird gleich noch etwas zum Bereich der Kulturschaffenden sagen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.400", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn dort ist das Thema von besonderer Brisanz."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.760", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Leistungen kosten Geld. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.480", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie bei Kranken- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.880", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Rentenversicherung fehlt Selbstst\u00e4ndigen der Arbeitgeberbeitrag. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.800", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch hier m\u00fcssen sie ihre Beitr\u00e4ge selbst erwirtschaften. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.560", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In welcher Gr\u00f6\u00dfenordnung das realistisch ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.440", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was in welchem Umfang \u00fcber welchen Zeitraum der Staat zuschie\u00dfen sollte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.640", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist eine der Fragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.320", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die l\u00e4ngst noch nicht beantwortet sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.400", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu gibt es auch in dem vorliegenden Antrag viele Ideen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.640", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.960", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich finde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.320", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "noch ein bisschen wenig Substanz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.880", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was die Finanzierung angeht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.600", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.720", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kommen Sie bitte zum Schluss."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.320", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb freue ich mich \u00fcber die Debatte im Ausschuss."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.120", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
